data.description: Your Dream Waterfront Oasis Awaits! Immerse yourself in refined elegance in this 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom sanctuary. The crown jewel of this residence is the unparalleled canal frontage, complete with a new 24k lb boat lift and ~58' of new seawall, offering seamless ocean access. Step inside to experience the spacious living areas, illuminated by tons of natural light, with tile flooring throughout. Marvel at the attention to detail in the updated kitchen featuring a waterfall island and all new stainless steel appliances.Outside, a heated salt pool, equipped with automation and a water feature, invites you to unwind amidst the lush turf and enchanting landscape lighting. Relish in unparalleled privacy with a comprehensive privacy wall and fencing, enhanced by a Mosquito Nix system for a pleasant outdoor experience. Enjoy the added conveniences of a whole-house automatic generator and on-demand gas water heater.Nestled in an environment that offers the best waterfront living, your lifestyle is enhanced by limitless opportunities for boating and fishing--right from your backyard: automatic front gates, circular driveway, and awning-covered parking round out this unparalleled offering. Elevate your life with this matchless blend of luxury and oceanic freedom!
